    <item>
      <title>Koji Typeface</title>
      <link>/project/koji/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Jan 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/project/koji/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ve been sketching out font ideas in the margins of college notebooks for years, so I thought it might be time to formalize one of them. The result is Koji, a typeface based off of a simple jig I would draw in my workbooks during class.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div align=&#34;center&#34;&gt;







  
  


&lt;div class=&#34;gallery&#34;&gt;

  
  
  
  
    
    
    
    
    
  &lt;a data-fancybox=&#34;gallery-images_koji&#34; href=&#34;/project/koji/images_koji/koji_alpha_numerals.png&#34; &gt;
  &lt;img data-src=&#34;/project/koji/images_koji/koji_alpha_numerals_hua0aeed18e879f0f4ecb4170aa1339690_166170_0x190_resize_lanczos_2.png&#34; class=&#34;lazyload&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; width=&#34;190&#34; height=&#34;190&#34;&gt;
  &lt;/a&gt;
  
    
    
    
    
    
  &lt;a data-fancybox=&#34;gallery-images_koji&#34; href=&#34;/project/koji/images_koji/koji_examples.png&#34; &gt;
  &lt;img data-src=&#34;/project/koji/images_koji/koji_examples_hu476c5b48e77f707c64c24d0da703d554_751339_0x190_resize_lanczos_2.png&#34; class=&#34;lazyload&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; width=&#34;118&#34; height=&#34;190&#34;&gt;
  &lt;/a&gt;
  
    
    
    
    
    
  &lt;a data-fancybox=&#34;gallery-images_koji&#34; href=&#34;/project/koji/images_koji/koji_jig.png&#34; &gt;
  &lt;img data-src=&#34;/project/koji/images_koji/koji_jig_hu741cd1bea51995d33a30b7b25514f419_39593_0x190_resize_lanczos_2.png&#34; class=&#34;lazyload&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; width=&#34;281&#34; height=&#34;190&#34;&gt;
  &lt;/a&gt;
  
    
    
    
    
    
  &lt;a data-fancybox=&#34;gallery-images_koji&#34; href=&#34;/project/koji/images_koji/koji_name.png&#34; &gt;
  &lt;img data-src=&#34;/project/koji/images_koji/koji_name_huaf9d58f78fb1c8a972ed3eecdf54a1e4_54949_0x190_resize_lanczos_2.png&#34; class=&#34;lazyload&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; width=&#34;190&#34; height=&#34;190&#34;&gt;
